Here, we learn to create Arrays in CSharp.
array decaration -> int[] numbers = new int[5];
length of array -> numbers.Length
array without array size declaration -> string[] names = new string[] {"Hema","Trishul","Abhay"}
To iterate thhru array: foreach(string name in names)
{
Console.WriteLine(name);
}
Reversing array->
Convert string array to CharArray. use ToCharArray()
use Array.Reverse(CharArray) to reverse array
display using foreach
